sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as LLSD Controller<br/>redhat-ods-applications
    participant LLSDPod as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,LLSDPod: Flow 1: LLSD Instance Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (new LLSD CR)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Service (ClusterIP :8321)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create PVC, SA, RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token

    Note over User,LLSDPod: Flow 2: Health Check and Status Update

    loop Periodic Health Check
        Operator->>LLSDPod: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321, plaintext, no auth
        LLSDPod-->>Operator: Health Status
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update LLSD status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    end

    Note over User,LLSDPod: Flow 3: ConfigMap Change Rollout

    User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: ConfigMap watch event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment annotations<br/>(trigger rolling restart)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI->>LLSDPod: Rolling restart of pods
